summary: This Simple Mod adds a Fletcher to the Slums of Windhelm Shop, That has a High Elf with THOUSANDS of EVERY TYPE of Arrow, and 60,000 Gold. Also Sells Many Different Kinds of Bows.
descriptionHtml:
This Simple Mod adds a Fletcher to the Slums of Windhelm Shop, That has a High Elf with THOUSANDS of EVERY TYPE of Arrow, (Included Modded Arrows) and 60,000 Gold. Also Sells Many Different Kinds of Bows.

Good Place to stock up on massive arrow buys in bulk!!
author: sw33tsp0t
